stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle: container start

    state Idle {
        [*] --> waiting
        waiting: model not loaded
    }

    note right of Idle
        VRAM = 0 GB
        Waiting for first request
    end note

    Idle --> Loading: request arrives

    state Loading {
        [*] --> cache_check
        cache_check: model cached?
        cache_check --> load_gpu: yes
        cache_check --> download_model: no
        download_model --> load_gpu
        load_gpu: load model to GPU
        load_gpu --> warmup
        warmup: warm-up inference
    }

    note right of Loading
        ASR ~3.4 GB
        TTS ~2-3 GB
        Cold start ~5-8 s
    end note

    Loading --> Active: model ready

    state Active {
        [*] --> ready
        ready: ready for inference
        ready --> infer: request
        infer: run inference
        infer --> ready: response
    }

    note right of Active
        VRAM allocated
        Idle timer running
    end note

    Active --> Active: new request / reset timer
    Active --> Unloading: idle timeout

    state Unloading {
        [*] --> drop_model
        drop_model: del model
        drop_model --> clear_cache
        clear_cache: torch.cuda.empty_cache()
        clear_cache --> collect_gc
        collect_gc: gc.collect()
    }

    note right of Unloading
        VRAM released
        Other services can reuse memory
    end note

    Unloading --> Idle: back to idle
